parameters: You can save your current level and money data in the record crystal.
Saved data can be inherited by another save data.
If you bought a house or furniture, you will get your money back.
If you want to carry over saved data, after starting a new game
Change your job to [Adventurer] and then open the transfer box next to it.
After starting a new game and changing jobs to an adventurer
Please open the transfer box next to it.
The transfer box cannot be opened with save data saved in the record crystal.
You can obtain the level and money stored in the record crystal.
Your level will increase, but the skills are still in the state you haven't acquired them, so please acquire them again.
Are you sure you want to transfer the recorded data?
The transfer box can only be opened by [Adventurer] players.
